@startuml ACO+自适应参数流程图
title ACO + 自适应参数调整流程

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
skinparam activityBorderColor #4A90D9
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFE4B5
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #DAA520

start

:初始化参数;
note right
  初始值：
  • α = 0.5
  • β = 3.5
  • ρ = 0.5
  • Q = 100
end note

:iteration = 1;

repeat

  #LightBlue:自适应参数调整;
  note right
    ratio = iter / max_iter
    α = 0.5 + 1.5 × ratio
    β = 3.5 - 2.0 × ratio
    ─────────────────
    前期：α小、β大（探索）
    后期：α大、β小（利用）
  end note

  :蚁群构建路径（使用新α, β）;

  if (当前最优 < 全局最优?) then (是)
    :更新全局最优解;
  else (否)
  endif

  :信息素更新;

  :记录收敛数据;

  :iteration++;

repeat while (iteration < max_iter?) is (是)
->否;

:输出结果;

stop

@enduml
